GSD.description:
eth: alx: take rtnl_lock on resume

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.15.75 by commit 6f1991a940b90753b34570f093a21dba366e8cc0, it was introduced in version v5.14 by commit 4a5fe57e775188be96359a1934501be45fe5f705. For more details please see the references link.
